{"tid":301264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習總訪港】匿名境外來電轟炸 斷金紫荊佔領者通訊","createTime":"2017-06-28T13:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T15:15:25.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ae725e576d18d8ef043ab20f956bfd449bd6e37","tid":301264,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T13:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170628/large/1498653462_ac58.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170628%2Flarge%2F1498653462_ac58.png&h=989867c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平本月29日至7月1日將訪港，灣仔金紫荊廣場繼兩日前清晨遭黑布包圍後，逾20名自決派下午5時許再次佔領金紫荊雕像，其中爬上雕像的社民連主席吳文遠表示，一眾留守雕像的示威者，晚上不約而同遭匿名來電密集式滋擾。<br />\n<br />\n吳文遠指，現場暫時共有7名示威者遭來電滋擾，接聽後對方自動播放錄音：「呢個係海外嘅來電&hellip;&hellip;」、「（錄音）句說話都未講完，下一個call又入嚟」，情況一直持續，直至示威者熄機。<br />\n他又指，匿名來電幾乎每秒打入一次，導致示威者無法與外界通訊，「搞到個電話用都用唔到」。同樣佔領雕像的眾志黃之鋒、羅冠聰，以及社民連梁國雄、黃浩銘等人一同遭殃。"},{"pid":"857ed52fbb04d978f1daa04064132599c0da0245","tid":301264,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T13:25:18.000Z","msg":"唔識用app block ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e5c7de20e1f34a7b10a45a873a396a2de9c491","tid":301264,"uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T13:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識用app block ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nunknown <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f1f9aa5c41a2dc04a0f3ecab6dd430577e75e4","tid":301264,"uid":29514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T13:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0tnp7uic\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0tnp7uic&h=9045